data.description: Take advantage of a 3% Seller-Paid Rate Buydown, offering you an even easier path to homeownership (terms and conditions apply). Ready to light up your life? This 3BR/2BA, 1366 sqft fixer-upper has been pre-smoked and rigorously de-flamed for your convenience! Say goodbye to the old carpet you didn't like anyway and hello to a bare-bones beauty, stripped down to the studs and raring to be dressed up. You know how people love 'open-concept'? Well, it doesn't get more open than this! We've taken care to prepare this home for its next chapter. Every surface has been thoroughly cleaned, and a fresh coat of heavy duty primer paint throughout the interior. Now, the place smells less like last year and more like your next big project. If you're someone who sees potential where others see work, this property is your canvas.
